**WU count: 12 → Critique tier: Full** (≥6 WUs).
**Risk-pattern triggers:** security-sensitive (hooks, allowlist enforcement), schema-shaped change (state schema). `tier = max(scope_tier, risk_tier) = Full`.

**Critical path:** WU2 → WU8 → WU12 → WU4 → WU5/WU6/WU7 (parallel after WU4) → WU9 → done. Length ≈ 7.

**Max parallel width:** ~4 (WU1, WU2, WU3, WU11 can all run in parallel as starting work; WU5/WU6/WU7 after WU4 land also yields width 3).

